Capacitive Touch Screen
------------------------

|product| is equipped with a multi-point capacitive touch screen. Its multi-point touch detection capability enables implementation of some advanced GUI operations, such as 
two-finger zoom or rotation. It can be operated by fingers, gloves with a special conductive coating, or a pen stylus designed for capacitive touch panels.

.. container:: hatnote hatnote-yellow

  |br|
  **Size/Type:** |dispsize| multi-point capacitive touch screen |br|
  **Surface Hardness:** 7H |br|
  **Service Life:** 50 million touch events |br|
  **Light Transmittance:** > 92%

\  